    "rationale": "All 13 ASME V&V 40 credibility factors assessed. Twelve of thirteen factors meet or exceed required levels. The single below-requirement factor (Test conditions, achieved 2 vs. required 3) is accepted on the basis that the single ASTM F1717 compression-bending configuration represents the conservative worst-case loading scenario for the device. Validation metrics E/uval < 1.96 and percent difference < 10% satisfied for all three QoIs across both laboratories. The package is submitted under ProfileMinimal with hash-based content integrity; cryptographic signature is pending completion of the institutional signature workflow and will be appended prior to final regulatory submission.",
